Apparently, Pelosi believes that we all have short memories or that we failed to follow the ridiculous process of the passage of Obamacare. 
Pelosi tweeted on Tuesday that the drafting process for the Affordable Care Act (a.k.a. Obamacare) was “one of the most transparent in recent memory.”   
